    "Name": "Striker",
    "Details": "n order to make the Striker more heat-efficient, the House Steiner variant removed the Large Laser and autocannon to incorporate an Autocannon/10 with a two-ton magazine. The result is a 'Mech that has less damage potential, but easier heat management.\n\n<b><color=#e62e00>Quirk: Easy to Maintain</color></b>\n\n<b><color=#e62e00>Drop Cost Multiplier: 1.12</color></b>\n\n<br><br><color=#FFEF00>Arm Actuator Limit: Left Lower</color>",
